title: Leopard in Palwal: Leopard spotted in Palwal city; wildlife officials reach the spot | Gurgaon News - Times of India
text:
GURUGRAM: A leopard was spotted in Palwal city on Thursday morning. 

A team of wildlife officials has reached the spot along with tranquilizers and vets. 

The leopard is currently in a house and the wildlife team is trying to rescue the big cat. 

One of the forest guards got injured while rescuing the leopard. He has been taken to Ram Manohar Lohia Hospital in New Delhi.
